# Technology Stack & Module Standards

## Purpose
Define the approved stack, versions, and allowed module choices.
This file owns dependency/version policy for runtime and tooling.

## Language and Module System
- Source code is JavaScript only (`.js`, `.jsx`).
- ES modules are required in `src/**`.
- Module-system exceptions are owned by `coding-conventions.mdc`.

